data.title: K1 Speed
data.meta_description: Looking for high-speed thrills and excitement in Tampa Bay? Look no further than K1 Speed, the premier destination for indoor go-kart racing in the area. K1 Speed has modern all-electric go-karts that can reach speeds of up to 45 miles per hour, giving you the ultimate adrenaline rush on our large professionally designed track. The K1 Speed Tampa Bay facility offers a range of options for groups of most ages and sizes, from junior karts for kids to adult karts for teens and adults. K1 also has a party room, arcade, and Paddock Lounge cafe that serves food and drinks, making K1 Speed the perfect location for your next event or celebration. So, whether you’re looking for a fun day out with friends, a unique birthday party idea, or a team-building activity for your company, K1 Speed in Tampa Bay has everything you need for a thrilling and memorable experience.
